Language: Batch
Name: Restore old right-click menu in Windows 11
Description: This script restores the original right click menu found in Windows 10 for all Windows 11 systems.
Customizable: No
@ECHO OFF
REG ADD "HKCU\Software\Classes\CLSID\{86ca1aa0-34aa-4e8b-a509-50c905bae2a2}\InprocServer32" /F /VE